## Project Vision
This project is powered by the **Kaven Framework**, a high-performance SaaS boilerplate.
Architecture: Next.js (App Router) + Fastify (API) + Prisma + PostgreSQL.

## 🛠 Core Commands
- `pnpm dev`: Start all services (Turborepo)
- `kaven module activate <name>`: Activate a schema module
- `kaven config features`: Open the feature flag TUI
- `pnpm db:migrate`: Run Prisma migrations

## 🧬 Coding Standards
- **Naming**: camelCase for variables/functions, PascalCase for components/classes.
- **Language**: Source code in **English**, comments and logs in **Portuguese (PT-BR)**.
- **Imports**: Use Absolute Imports (`@/lib/...`).
- **Prisma**: Never modify `schema.prisma` directly; use `schema.extended.prisma`.

## 🤖 Agent Instructions
- **Handoffs**: Always end sessions with a session digest in `.aiox/sessions/`.
- **Integrity**: Before merging any code, run `kaven module doctor`.
- **Memory**: Save recurring architectural decisions to MCP memory.

